card.text:
Playable on Cirdan or Gandalf. If in company with Cirdan or Gandalf, Treebeard and/or Tom Bombadil may move to Tom’s House and/or Wellinghall without being discarded. If both are in the same company, place them “off to the side.” You may tap them both to either:
	- Cancel Rolled Down to the Sea or The Balance of Things; 
	- Give +2 to a ring test, or to bring Cracks of Doom, Favor of the Valar, or The Old Thrush to your hand from discard pile;
	- Store Fate of the Ithil Stone or Into the Smoking Cone at Mount Doom or Barad-dur for full mp.
	- Make Awakened Plant creatures playable against minion companies at Cirdan or Gandalf’s current site;
	- Discard The Will of Sauron or Shadow of Mordor. Discard if Tom Bombadil or Treebeard leaves play. Cannot be duplicated on a given player.
